The paper proposes a method for task-oriented dialog systems in the context of visual dialog, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed method involves maximizing information gain, which is a common approach in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The evaluation is based on a visual dialog task, which is a type of machine learning problem (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves generating questions, which is a common task in information retrieval (cs.IR).
